&lt;li&gt;Learn our product by getting certified with our SpotMe Academy and by embedding yourself in a virtual event project, an onsite event project, by building your own demo event and by joining an in-person business review.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Become fluent with our industry personas, competitors, and our industry use cases by embedding yourself in customer projects and presentations.&lt;/li&gt;
